description:
*An edited, illustrated and narrated playthrough of the game Caves of Qud*

 Today, we blindly stumble into the overwhelming world of Caves of Qud as the fledgling adventurer known as Aecius Rudius. 

 Will we die immediately? Who could say?!

----------

Thanks to everyone who helped out with this episode!

title: Caves of Qud: Aecius' Quest
